snippet.title: Shark Attack game (PC)
snippet.description:
Play Shark Attack game, the classic deep-sea 2D adventure arcade game. 

Explore the underwater adventure and help Kenny, a brave young scuba diver, restore all the broken pieces in different parts of the world.

Features:
- Collect 4 different artifacts to advance to next level
- Avoid enemy creatures, jump on small beasts to throw them out
- Blow up mines to remove obstacles along the way
- Vibrant, cartoon-like visuals giving you more than 60 game levels in 3 diverse worlds

The full version game of Shark Attack is available at GameTop for free!
